n Fang","active":true,"timeZone":"America/Los_Angeles"},"created":"2015-03-17T22:51:26.189+0000","updated":"2015-03-17T22:51:26.189+0000"},{"self":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/rest/api/2/issue/12662238/comment/14570348","id":"14570348","author":{"self":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/rest/api/2/user?username=jiessie","name":"jiessie","key":"jiessie","avatarUrls":{"48x48":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?avatarId=10452","24x24":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=small&avatarId=10452","16x16":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=xsmall&avatarId=10452","32x32":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=medium&avatarId=10452"},"displayName":"Jie Cao","active":true,"timeZone":"Etc/UTC"},"body":"The root cause has been fixed in hadoop 2.7.1, see https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/MAPREDUCE-6238\n\nWorking around solutions for earlier hadoop version: \nSince this issue will occured when \"-libjars 1.jar -files 2.jar -archives 3.jar \" options are specified, for supporting local mode on earlier hadoop version, you can work around by make those 3 options empty, which are  generated from Hive options.\n\nsee ExecDriver.java:\n\"-libjars\" are generated from \"hive.aux.jars.path\" and \"hive.added.jars.path\"\n\"-files\" are generated from \"hive.added.files.path\"\n\"-archives\" are generated from \"hive.added.archives.path\"\n\nThen,  e.g.  \"set hive.aux.jars.path=;\"  can empty the \"-libjars\" options.\nHowever, some aux jars may be required that you can add those jars by setting \"HIVE_AUX_JARS_PATH\" in env.\nWhen setting \"HIVE_AUX_JARS_PATH\" in env, hcat command  will append those jars to the HADOOP_CLASSPATH and make it work in local mode.\n\n\n\n\n","updateAuthor":{"self":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/rest/api/2/user?username=jiessie","name":"jiessie","key":"jiessie","avatarUrls":{"48x48":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?avatarId=10452","24x24":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=small&avatarId=10452","16x16":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=xsmall&avatarId=10452","32x32":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=medium&avatarId=10452"},"displayName":"Jie Cao","active":true,"timeZone":"Etc/UTC"},"created":"2015-06-03T06:21:46.234+0000","updated":"2015-06-03T06:21:46.234+0000"}],"maxResults":12,"total":12,"startAt":0},"votes":{"self":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/rest/api/2/issue/HIVE-5016/votes","votes":0,"hasVoted":false},"worklog":{"startAt":0,"maxResults":20,"total":0,"worklogs":[]},"customfield_12311820":"0|i1n0uf:"}}